recommend keep-going -- the SLC product is named and compass-true, L1 already green; the one lap that unblocks L2 (live carriage) is Pool P0, the same keystone the roadmap already prioritizes. Ship this, then open Pool P0 -- finishing one real thing before naming the next, exactly the edge.
